abilityArray.title: Flying
abilityArray.body: When counting movement spaces for Kor Aeronaught Captain, ignore elevations. Kor Aeronaught Captain may fly over water without stopping, pass over figures without becoming engaged, and fly over obstacles such as ruins. When a Kor Aeronaught Captain starts to fly, it will take any leaving-engagement attacks.

abilityArray.title: Ride the currents
abilityArray.body: Whenever Kor Aeronaut Captain moves to a lower elevation during its movement for the first time each turn, it gets +3 move until end of turn.

abilityArray.title: Air Raid
abilityArray.body: Before moving Kor Aeronaut Captain, choose an adjacent small or medium squad creature you control. After you move Kor Aeronaut Captain, place the chosen squad creature on an empty space adjacent to Kor Aeronaut Captain. Use this ability once per turn.

abilityArray.title: SEA BORN
abilityArray.body: Kiora may move through water spaces without stopping movement, and she gets +2#{aotp aotp-defense} while in water.

abilityArray.title: carry by waves
abilityArray.body: At the start of Kiora's turn, move a creature you control up to 4 spaces.

abilityArray.title: bident of thassa
abilityArray.body: Once per game, when Kiora ends her turn in a water space, you may reveal the top 2 cards of your library. Put a sorcery from among them into your hand and the rest on the bottom of your library in any order.

abilityArray.title: Lash of Tentacles
abilityArray.body: At the start of Eldrazi Ruiner's turn, deal 1 damage to all adjacent non-Eldrazi creatures.

abilityArray.title: Otherworldy
abilityArray.body: While being attacked by a nonadjacent creature, Eldrazi Ruiner gets +2#{aotp aotp-defense}.

abilityArray.title: Shepard of Scions
abilityArray.body: Deal 1 damage to Eldrazi Ruiner and place an Eldrazi Scion creature from your figure graveyard on an adjacent empty space. Use this ability once per turn.

abilityArray.title: Devour for Speed
abilityArray.body: At the start of the turn of an Eldrazi hero creature you control, you may destroy an Eldrazi Scion creature you control. If you do, that Eldrazi hero creature gets +4 move until end of turn. Use this ability once per turn.

abilityArray.title: Devour for Strength
abilityArray.body: At the start of the turn of an Eldrazi hero creature you control, you may destroy an Eldrazi Scion creature you control. If you do, the Eldrazi hero creature gets +2 #{aotp aotp-attack} until end of turn. Use this ability once per turn.

abilityArray.title: Escort
abilityArray.body: Each small or medium creature you control adjacent to a Path Warden can be attacked only by adjacent figures.

abilityArray.title: Sea Born
abilityArray.body: Merfolk Roilmage may move through water spaces without stopping movement, and it gets +2#{aotp aotp-defense} while in water.

abilityArray.title: Part Waters
abilityArray.body: Friendly figures may move through empty water spaces adjacent to Merfolk Roilmage without stopping movement.

abilityArray.title: Flying
abilityArray.body: When counting movement spaces for Ob Nixilis, ignore elevations. Ob Nixilis may fly over water without stopping, pass over figures without becoming engaged, and fly over obstacles such as ruins. When Ob Nixilis starts to fly, he will take any leaving-engagement attacks.

abilityArray.title: At Any Price
abilityArray.body: Destroy target squad creature adjacent to Ob Nixilis. Its controller draws a card. Use this ability once per turn.

abilityArray.title: Lifelink
abilityArray.body: While attacking with a Malakir Bloodchaser, for each damage it deals to the defending figure, remove a damage marker from the Malakir Bloodchaser.

abilityArray.title: Scent of Blood
abilityArray.body: While attacking, a Malakir Bloodchaser gets +1 hit if the defending figure has a damage marker on it.

abilityArray.title: Volatile Hedron Javelin
abilityArray.body:
Choose a Goblin Javelineer you control and a target creature up to 6 clear sight spaces away from it. Roll the 20-sided die:

1-3, Deal 1 damage to the chosen Goblin Javelineer

4-15, Deal 1 damage to the chosen target creature.

16-20, Deal 2 damage to the chosen target creature.

Use this ability once per turn.
